title: Temperance Movement @ The Crossroads Festival Bonn 2017
description:
MPEG2 720P Audio 320 @ 41000 Hz

If you liked the Rolling Stones in the Early Years, you will LOVE this band from Glasgow Scotland.  Blues and Rock and much more LIVE at the Crossroads Festival in Bonn Germany 2017.  Includes 2 bonus Video's.  All tracks are edited into Music Video's designed for easy import into professional DJ and Club playout software.
